/sys/class/thermal/thermal_zone0/temp
50000
5000

1st row: path to file where to read from current temperature
2nd row: minimal temperature from where to start cooler (in K * 1000)
3d  row: hysteresis difference between 2nd row temperature and temperature, 
on which we should stop cooler (K*1000)
other lines are ignored.
NOTE, that after "make install" this file is placed to /etc/cooldown/
